item.title: About
item.description: The Story: Originally started in December of 2014 this site began as a side hobby of mine and has quickly grown into one of the most successful side projects I’ve ever worked upon. Since its conception it’s racked up well over 1,000,000 page views and it’s still growing. It’s undergone many changes since it was first created and overall I’ve probably commited well over 1,000 hours towards the site and it’s content.
